  "title": "Welcome, Java 9!",
  "summary": "Java 9 is out today and with other members of the community I'm throwing a welcome party. Get an all around view on the new Java release with various opinions, tips, and great sources!",
  "content": "<p>Java 9 is out today and with other members of the community I&#x27;m throwing a welcome party. Get an all around view on the new Java release with various opinions, tips, and great sources!</p><p>Simon Maple:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/sjmaple\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zeroturnaround.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ZeroTurnaround</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.joda.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Joda projects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.manning.com/books/the-java-module-system?a_aid=nipa&amp;a_bid=869915cb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">modularity</a> <a href=\"https://javamodularity.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">books</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Stephen Colebourne:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/jodastephen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://blog.joda.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://strata.opengamma.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OpenGamma</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.joda.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Joda projects</a></li>\n<li>on modules and their names: <a href=\"http://blog.joda.org/2017/04/java-se-9-jpms-module-naming.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1</a>, <a href=\"http://blog.joda.org/2017/04/java-se-9-jpms-modules-are-not-artifacts.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Christian Stein:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/sormuras\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://junit.org/junit5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JUnit 5</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sormuras/bach\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bach (JShell-based build tool)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nicolai Parlog:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nipafx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nipafx.dev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.manning.com/books/the-java-module-system?a_aid=nipa&amp;a_bid=869915cb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>The Java Module System</em></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Trisha Gee:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/trisha_gee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://trishagee.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://trishagee.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JetBrains</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GkP83hvdeMk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>Real World Java 9</em></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Chris Engelbert:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/noctarius2k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hazelcast.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hazelcast</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Sander Mak:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Sander_Mak\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://branchandbound.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.luminis.eu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Luminis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://javamodularity.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>Java 9 Modularity</em></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Jens Schauder:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/jensschauder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://blog.schauderhaft.de/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://projects.spring.io/spring-data-jpa/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spring Data</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pivotal.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Pivotal</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Monica Beckwith:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/mon_beck\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.codekaram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Code Karam</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Rafael Winterhalter:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/rafaelcodes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://rafael.codes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Site</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://bytebuddy.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ByteBuddy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://mockito.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mockito</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/javazone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JavaZone talks</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Wayne Beaton:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/waynebeaton\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eclipse.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Eclipse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.eclipse.org/openj9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OpenJ9</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wiki.eclipse.org/java9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Eclipse support for Java 9</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Simon Ritter:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/speakjava\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://azul.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Azul Systems</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CMMzG8I23lY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>55 New Features in JDK 9</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.azul.com/jdk-9-pitfalls-for-the-unwary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>JDK 9: Pitfalls For The Unwary</em></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.azul.com/jdk-9-xxtra-command-line-options/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>JDK 9: XXtra Command Line Options</em></a></li>\n</ul><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sjIdWNHrMs4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Watch the video.</a></p>",
